ntibodies\">Asthma Antibodies</a></li>\n              <li class=\"mb-2\"><a href=\"https://SITE_ORIGIN_PLACEHOLDER/diseases/autism-spectrum-disorder-antibodies\">Autism Spectrum Disorder Antibodies</a></li>\n              <li class=\"mb-2\"><a href=\"https://SITE_ORIGIN_PLACEHOLDER/diseases/bipolar-disorder-antibodies\">Bipolar Disorder Antibodies</a></li>\n              <li class=\"mb-2\"><a href=\"https://SITE_ORIGIN_PLACEHOLDER/diseases/breast-cancer-antibodies\">Breast Cancer Antibodies</a></li>\n              <li class=\"mb-2\"><a href=\"https://SITE_ORIGIN_PLACEHOLDER/diseases/cardiovascular-disease-antibodies\">Cardiovascular Disease Antibodies</a></li>\n              <li class=\"mb-2\"><a href=\"https://SITE_ORIGIN_PLACEHOLDER/diseases/cholangiocarcinoma-antibodies\">Cholangiocarcinoma Antibodies</a></li>\n              <li class=\"mb-2\"><a href=\"https://SITE_ORIGIN_PLACEHOLDER/diseases/chronic-obstructive-pulmonary-disease-copd-antibodies\">COPD Antibodies</a></li>\n              <li class=\"mb-2\"><a href=\"https://SITE_ORIGIN_PLACEHOLDER/diseases/colorectal-cancer-antibodies\">Colorectal Cancer Antibodies</a></li>\n              <li class=\"mb-2\"><a href=\"https://SITE_ORIGIN_PLACEHOLDER/diseases/crohn-s-disease-antibodies\">Crohn's Disease Antibodies</a></li>\n              <li class=\"mb-2\"><a href=\"https://SITE_ORIGIN_PLACEHOLDER/diseases/cystic-fibrosis-antibodies\">Cystic Fibrosis Antibodies</a></li>\n              <li class=\"mb-2\"><a href=\"https://SITE_ORIGIN_PLACEHOLDER/diseases/depression-antibodies\">Depression Antibodies</a></li>\n              <li class=\"mb-2\"><a href=\"https://SITE_ORIGIN_PLACEHOLDER/diseases/diabetes-mellitus-antibodies\">Diabetes Mellitus Antibodies</a></li>\n              <li class=\"mb-0\"><a href=\"https://SITE_ORIGIN_PLACEHOLDER/diseases/endometrial-cancer-antibodies\">Endometrial Cancer Antibodies</a></li>\n            </ul>\n\n            <ul class=\"list-unstyled col-12 col-lg-4 mb-0 mt-4 mt-lg-0\">\n              <li class=\"mb-2\"><a href=\"https://SITE_ORIGIN_PLACEHOLDER/diseases/endometriosis-antibodies\">Endometriosis Antibodies</a></li>\n              <li class=\"mb-2\"><a href=\"https://SITE_ORIGIN_PLACEHOLDER/diseases/epilepsy-antibodies\">Epilepsy Antibodies</a></li>\n              <li class=\"mb-2\"><a href=\"https://SITE_ORIGIN_PLACEHOLDER/diseases/esophageal-cancer-antibodies\">Esophageal Cancer Antibodies</a></li>\n              <li class=\"mb-2\"><a href=\"https://SITE_ORIGIN_PLACEHOLDER/diseases/fibromyalgia-antibodies\">Fibromyalgia Antibodies</a></li>\n              <li class=\"mb-2\"><a href=\"https://SITE_ORIGIN_PLACEHOLDER/diseases/gastric-cancer-antibodies\">Gastric Cancer Antibodies</a></li>\n              <li class=\"mb-2\"><a href=\"https://SITE_ORIGIN_PLACEHOLDER/diseases/glioblastoma-antibodies\">Glioblastoma Antibodies</a></li>\n              <li class=\"mb-2\"><a href=\"https://SITE_ORIGIN_PLACEHOLDER/diseases/head-and-neck-cancer-antibodies\">Head and Neck Cancer Antibodies</a></li>\n              <li class=\"mb-2\"><a href=\"https://SITE_ORIGIN_PLACEHOLDER/diseases/heart-disease-antibody\">Heart Disease Antibody</a></li>\n              <li class=\"mb-2\"><a href=\"https://SITE_ORIGIN_PLACEHOLDER/diseases/hypertension-antibodies\">Hypertension Antibodies</a></li>\n              <li class=\"mb-2\"><a href=\"https://SITE_ORIGIN_PLACEHOLDER/diseases/liver-cancer-antibodies\">Liver Cancer Antibodies</a></li>\n              <li class=\"mb-2\"><a href=\"https://SITE_ORIGIN_PLACEHOLDER/diseases/lung-cancer-antibody\">Lung Cancer Antibody</a></li>\n              <li class=\"mb-2\"><a href=\"https://SITE_ORIGIN_PLACEHOLDER/diseases/lymphoma-antibodies\">Lymphoma Antibodies</a></li>\n              <li class=\"mb-2\"><a href=\"https://SITE_ORIGIN_PLACEHOLDER/diseases/melanoma-antibody\">Melanoma Antibody</a></li>\n              <li class=\"mb-2\"><a href=\"https://SITE_ORIGIN_PLACEHOLDER/diseases/multiple-myeloma-antibodies\">Multiple Myeloma Antibodies</a></li>\n              <li class=\"mb-2\"><a href=\"https://SITE_ORIGIN_PLACEHOLDER/diseases/multiple-sclerosis-antibody\">Multiple Sclerosis Antibody</a></li>\n              <li class=\"mb-2\"><a href=\"https://SITE_ORIGIN_PLACEHOLDER/diseases/myasthenia-gravis-antibodies\">Myasthenia Gravis Antibodies</a></li>\n              <li class=\"mb-0\"><a href=\"https://SITE_ORIGIN_PLACEHOLDER/diseases/myelodysplastic-syndrome-antibodies\">Myelodysplastic Syndrome Antibodies</a></li>\n            </ul>\n\n            <ul class=\"list-unstyled col-12 col-lg-4 mb-0 mt-4 mt-lg-0\">\n              <li class=\"mb-2\"><a href=\"https://SITE_ORIGIN_PLACEHOLDER/diseases/nephrotic-syndrome-antibodies\">Nephrotic Syndrome Antibodies</a></li>\n              <li class=\"mb-2\"><a href=\"https://SITE_ORIGIN_PLACEHOLDER/diseases/non-hodgkin-lymphoma-antibodies\">Non-Hodgkin Lymphoma Antibodies</a></li>\n              <li class=\"mb-2\"><a href=\"https://SITE_ORIGIN_PLACEHOLDER/diseases/osteosarcoma-antibodies\">Osteosarcoma Antibodies</a></li>\n              <li class=\"mb-2\"><a href=\"https://SITE_ORIGIN_PLACEHOLDER/diseases/ovarian-cancer-antibodies\">Ovarian Cancer Antibodies</a></li>\n              <li class=\"mb-2\"><a href=\"https://SITE_ORIGIN_PLACEHOLDER/diseases/pancreatic-cancer-antibody\">Pancreatic Cancer Antibody</a></li>\n              <li class=\"mb-2\"><a href=\"https://SITE_ORIGIN_PLACEHOLDER/diseases/parkinson-s-disease-antibody\">Parkinson's Disease Antibody</a></li>\n              <li class=\"mb-2\"><a href=\"https://SITE_ORIGIN_PLACEHOLDER/diseases/prostate-cancer-antibody\">Prostate Cancer Antibody</a></li>\n              <li class=\"mb-2\"><a href=\"https://SITE_ORIGIN_PLACEHOLDER/diseases/rheumatoid-arthritis-antibody\">Rheumatoid Arthritis Antibody</a></li>\n              <li class=\"mb-2\"><a href=\"https://SITE_ORIGIN_PLACEHOLDER/diseases/sjogren-s-syndrome-antibodies\">Sjögren's Syndrome Antibodies</a></li>\n              <li class=\"mb-2\"><a href=\"https://SITE_ORIGIN_PLACEHOLDER/diseases/stomach-cancer-antibody\">Stomach Cancer Antibody</a></li>\n              <li class=\"mb-2\"><a href=\"https://SITE_ORIGIN_PLACEHOLDER/diseases/systemic-sclerosis-antibodies\">Systemic Sclerosis Antibodies</a></li>\n              <li class=\"mb-2\"><a href=\"https://SITE_ORIGIN_PLACEHOLDER/diseases/thyroid-cancer-antibody\">Thyroid Cancer Antibody</a></li>\n              <li class=\"mb-2\"><a href=\"https://SITE_ORIGIN_PLACEHOLDER/diseases/chronic-lymphocytic-leukemia-antibodies\">Chronic Lymphocytic Leukemia Antibodies</a></li>\n              <li class=\"mb-0\"><a href=\"https://SITE_ORIGIN_PLACEHOLDER/diseases/acute-myeloid-leukemia-antibodies\">Acute Myeloid Leukemia Antibodies</a></li>\n            </ul>\n\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"mb-6 single-column content-section\">\n  <div class=\"container\">\n    <div class=\"row\">\n      <div class=\"col-12\">\n        <h2 class=\"font-large text-orange mb-2 text-capitalize\">Browse by Cell Type</h2>\n        <p class=\"font-medium text-grey mb-4\">\n          Use these cell-type entry points to move quickly across tissue context, lineage, and experimental systems used in multiple research fields.\n        </p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"col-12\">\n        <div class=\"p-4\" style=\"background:#fafafa; border:1px solid #ececec; border-radius:10px;\">\n          <div class=\"row list\">\n            <ul class=\"list-unstyled col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-4 mb-0\">\n              <li class=\"mb-2\"><a href=\"https://SITE_ORIGIN_PLACEHOLDER/cell-types/adipocytes-antibodies\">Adipocytes Antibodies</a></li>\n              <li class=\"mb-2\"><a href=\"https://SITE_ORIGIN_PLACEHOLDER/cell-types/b-cell-antibodies\">B-Cell Antibodies</a></li>\n              <li class=\"mb-2\"><a href=\"https://SITE_ORIGIN_PLACEHOLDER/cell-types/cardiomyocytes-antibodies\">Cardiomyocytes Antibodies</a></li>\n              <li class=\"mb-2\"><a href=\"https://SITE_ORIGIN_PLACEHOLDER/cell-types/chondrocytes-antibodies\">Chondrocytes Antibodies</a></li>\n              <li class=\"mb-2\"><a href=\"https://SITE_ORIGIN_PLACEHOLDER/cell-types/dendritic-cells-antibodies\">Dendritic Cells Antibodies</a></li>\n              <li class=\"mb-2\"><a href=\"https://SITE_ORIGIN_PLACEHOLDER/cell-types/endothelial-cells-antibodies\">Endothelial Cells Antibodies</a></li>\n              <li class=\"mb-2\"><a href=\"https://SITE_ORIGIN_PLACEHOLDER/cell-types/epithelial-cells-antibodies\">Epithelial Cells Antibodies</a></li>\n            </ul>\n            <ul class=\"list-unstyled col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-4 mb-0 mt-3 mt-md-0\">\n              <li class=\"mb-2\"><a href=\"https://SITE_ORIGIN_PLACEHOLDER/cell-types/fibroblasts-antibodies\">Fibroblasts Antibodies</a></li>\n              <li class=\"mb-2\"><a href=\"https://SITE_ORIGIN_PLACEHOLDER/cell-types/glial-cells-antibodies\">Glial Cells Antibodies</a></li>\n              <li class=\"mb-2\"><a href=\"https://SITE_ORIGIN_PLACEHOLDER/cell-types/hepatocytes-antibodies\">Hepatocytes Antibodies</a></li>\n              <li class=\"mb-2\"><a href=\"https://SITE_ORIGIN_PLACEHOLDER/cell-types/macrophage-antibodies\">Macrophage Antibodies</a></li>\n              <li class=\"mb-2\"><a href=\"https://SITE_ORIGIN_PLACEHOLDER/cell-types/mesenchymal-stem-cells-antibodies\">Mesenchymal Stem Cells Antibodies</a></li>\n              <li class=\"mb-2\"><a href=\"https://SITE_ORIGIN_PLACEHOLDER/cell-types/myeloid-related-entry-antibodies\">Myeloid-Related Entry Antibodies</a></li>\n              <li class=\"mb-2\"><a href=\"https://SITE_ORIGIN_PLACEHOLDER/cell-types/myocytes-antibodies\">Myocytes Antibodies</a></li>\n              <li class=\"mb-2\"><a href=\"https://SITE_ORIGIN_PLACEHOLDER/cell-types/neuron-antibodies\">Neuron Antibodies</a></li>\n            </ul>\n            <ul class=\"list-unstyled col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-4 mb-0 mt-3 mt-lg-0\">\n              <li class=\"mb-2\"><a h